<h2>Irrigator</h2>
<p>The Irrigator device provides flexible, sensor-based irrigation control for various plants or garden setups. Built on the Sensor Control Template.</p>

<h3>Template</h3>
<p>This device is based on the <a href="/templates/sensor-control">Sensor Control Template</a>, which enables automated control based on sensor feedback.</p>

<h3>Key Features</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Flexible Irrigation Control</li>
  <li>Adaptable to Different Containers and Gardens</li>
</ul>

<h3>Use Cases</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Home Gardens</li>
  <li>Outdoor Plant Care</li>
</ul>